<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <style>
        body { font-family: Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; color: #333; }
        .container { max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px; }
        .header { background: #10B981; color: white; padding: 20px; text-align: center; }
        .content { background: #f9fafb; padding: 30px; }
        .button { display: inline-block; padding: 12px 24px; background: #10B981; color: white; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 6px; margin: 20px 0; }
        .footer { text-align: center; padding: 20px; color: #666; font-size: 12px; }
        .success-box { background: #D1FAE5; border: 2px solid #10B981; padding: 15px; border-radius: 6px; margin: 20px 0; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <h1>✅ Invitation Accepted!</h1>
        </div>
        <div class="content">
            <p>Hi <%= clientName %>,</p>
            
            <div class="success-box">
                <h3 style="margin-top: 0; color: #059669;">Great News!</h3>
                <p style="margin-bottom: 0;"><strong><%= freelancerName %></strong> has accepted your invitation for "<strong><%= gigTitle %></strong>"!</p>
            </div>
            
            <p>You can now proceed with the gig assignment and escrow setup.</p>
            
            <h4>Next Steps:</h4>
            <ol>
                <li>Go to your gig dashboard</li>
                <li>Assign the gig to <%= freelancerName %></li>
                <li>Lock funds in escrow</li>
                <li>The freelancer can then start working</li>
            </ol>
            
            <a href="<%= actionUrl %>" class="button">Assign Gig Now</a>
            
            <p style="color: #666; font-size: 14px;">
                <strong>Reminder:</strong> Make sure to lock the agreed amount in escrow before the freelancer starts working. This protects both parties.
            </p>
        </div>
        <div class="footer">
            <p>© 2025 HireChain - Decentralized Freelancing on Hedera</p>
            <p>This is an automated notification. Please do not reply to this email.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
